<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:17:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战后数十年，朝鲜仍在修建边界并鸣枪警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/decades-after-war-north-korea-still-builds-borders-draws-warning-shots-2024-06-25/</link><description>朝鲜战争爆发 74 年后，朝鲜军队正在修建新的防御工事，偶尔会招致韩国军队越过一直处于战争状态的边境线发出警告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 05:25:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/decades-after-war-north-korea-still-builds-borders-draws-warning-shots-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>47名香港民主党人的里程碑式审判进入宣判前的最后阶段</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/landmark-trial-47-hong-kong-democrats-enters-final-stretch-before-sentencing-2024-06-25/</link><description>香港有史以来规模最大的针对香港民主反对派的国家安全审判的减刑请求于周二启动，预计这是宣判前的最后阶段，部分被告可能被判处终身监禁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 04:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/landmark-trial-47-hong-kong-democrats-enters-final-stretch-before-sentencing-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国反击西方电动汽车、锂电池产能过剩指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-its-evs-lithium-batteries-meet-domestic-demand-enrich-global-supply-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国总理李强在大连举行的世界经济论坛会议上发表讲话，回击了美国和欧盟的指控，即中国企业从不公平补贴中受益，并准备用廉价的绿色技术涌入其市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 03:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-its-evs-lithium-batteries-meet-domestic-demand-enrich-global-supply-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾外长表示希望与中国就南海问题进行对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-wants-talk-with-china-south-china-sea-foreign-minister-says-2024-06-25/</link><description>菲律宾外交部长恩里克·马纳洛周二表示，菲律宾正在努力让中国重返谈判桌，以解决南海分歧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 03:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-wants-talk-with-china-south-china-sea-foreign-minister-says-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市普遍走高，日元兑欧元创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-25/</link><description>亚洲股市在近期下跌后，周二大多走高，而遭受重创的日元兑欧元创下历史新低，尽管干预风险阻止了兑美元进一步走软。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 02:28:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在日本推出第三款电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-launches-third-ev-model-japan-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国比亚迪周二表示，在日本推出了第三款电动汽车，这款轿车将是该公司迄今为止在日本市场上最昂贵的车型，而消费者长期以来一直青睐国产品牌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 02:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-launches-third-ev-model-japan-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于干预威胁迫在眉睫，美元跌至 160 日元附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-flirts-with-key-160-yen-level-intervention-risk-looms-2024-06-25/</link><description>周二，美元试图突破 160 日元关键水平，但收效甚微，因为对日本官员货币干预的担忧使得日元兑其他货币受到小幅支撑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-flirts-with-key-160-yen-level-intervention-risk-looms-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>通胀担忧限制夏季需求乐观情绪，油价稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-steady-markets-weigh-supply-tensions-china-economic-recovery-2024-06-25/</link><description>继前一交易日上涨后，周二油价几乎没有变化，因为投资者在美国消费者价格数据公布之前保持谨慎，尽管预期的夏季需求增加支撑了市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-steady-markets-weigh-supply-tensions-china-economic-recovery-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国调查中国电信、中国移动互联网、云风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-probing-china-telecom-china-mobile-over-internet-cloud-risks-2024-06-25/</link><description>三名知情人士称，拜登政府正在调查中国移动、中国电信和中国联通，因为担心这些公司可能通过其美国云和互联网业务向北京提供美国数据。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-probing-china-telecom-china-mobile-over-internet-cloud-risks-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>普华永道表示，随着员工拥抱人工智能、提高技能，“伟大的辞职”进入第三个年头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/great-resignation-enters-third-year-workers-embrace-ai-upskilling-pwc-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>普华永道对全球劳动力的一项调查发现，预计在未来 12 个月内更换雇主的工人比例高于 2022 年“大辞职”时期的比例。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 23:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/great-resignation-enters-third-year-workers-embrace-ai-upskilling-pwc-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>年中购物节失败后中国零售前景黯淡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-retail-outlook-dims-after-mid-year-shopping-festival-flop-2024-06-24/</link><description>在经历了令人失望的年中网上购物节之后，中国零售商面临着令人畏惧的近期未来，这也给世界第二大经济体的复苏前景蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 23:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-retail-outlook-dims-after-mid-year-shopping-festival-flop-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国驳回加拿大对新疆人权问题的投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dismisses-canadian-complaints-over-xinjiang-human-rights-2024-06-24/</link><description>中国周一驳回了加拿大关于渥太华所说的关于西部新疆地区侵犯人权行为的“可信报告”的投诉，并表示渥太华应该关注自己的歧视问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 20:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dismisses-canadian-complaints-over-xinjiang-human-rights-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国外交官称，美国需要中国人文学科学生和印度科学学生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-needs-chinese-students-humanities-indian-students-sciences-us-diplomat-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>这位排名第二的美国外交官周一表示，美国应该欢迎更多来自中国的学生，但应该学习人文学科而不是科学，并指出出于安全考虑，美国大学正在限制中国学生接触敏感技术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 18:15:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-needs-chinese-students-humanities-indian-students-sciences-us-diplomat-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>白宫官员表示，微软与 G42 的协议是积极的，因为它切断了与华为的联系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-g42-deal-positive-because-it-cut-huawei-ties-white-house-official-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>一位白宫官员周一表示，微软向人工智能公司 G42 投资 15 亿美元的交易“总体上是一个积极的进展”，因为它迫使这家总部位于阿拉伯联合酋长国的公司断绝了与中国华为的关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 16:39:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-g42-deal-positive-because-it-cut-huawei-ties-white-house-official-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item><item><title>印度 Amara Raja 与中国国轩签署锂离子电池制造许可协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-amara-raja-inks-licensing-deal-with-chinas-gotion-lithium-ion-cell-2024-06-24/</link><description>印度电池制造商Amara Raja Energy and Mobility周一表示，该公司与中国国轩高科技公司旗下子公司Gotion-InoBat-Batteries (GIB)签署了一项许可协议，在印度生产锂离子电池。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:53:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-amara-raja-inks-licensing-deal-with-chinas-gotion-lithium-ion-cell-2024-06-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>